 Even in the Vedayana Gurbia Masambhata says, see, see, obstacle is our mind. Gurbia Masambhata said

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:33.800
, obstacle is our mind, that obstacle come from mind.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:47.800
 So that conception is demon, that that demon come from mind. That's what the Gurbia Masambhata said

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.800
. So in Vedayana teaching, that is.

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:54.800
 So from now on, from the Hine there is no difference.

00:07:54.800 --> 00:08:07.750
 This phenomenon ego is particularly that to remove. This is then special teachings of the Mahayana

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:09.800
 and that's what is Vedayana.

